if given linear data structure
if ask for longest/shortest substring/subarray or desire value
- sliding window

if given linear data structure
if array item equal pair/triplet/subarray
- two pointer

if given linear data structure loop
if ask for item position or data structure length
- fast and slow pointer

if given overlap interval
if ask for list with mutual exclusive interval
- merge interval

if given sort linear data structure
if ask for missing/duplicate/smallest value within sort/rotate data structure
- cyclic sort

if ask for reverse link list without extra memory utilization
- in place link list reversal

if ask for tree traversal within each level
- breadth first search

if ask for tree traversal with inorder/preorder/postorder depth first search
if ask for leaf search
- depth first search

if given priority data structure
if ask for smallest/largest/median item within set
if given binary tree data structure
- two heap

if ask for set combination/permutation
- subset

if given sort linear data structure
if ask for specific item
- binary search

if ask for top/smallest/frequent "k" item within set
if ask to sort linear data structure for specific item
- top "k" item

if given sort linear data structure
if ask to merge sort linear data structure and search smallest item within data structure
- k-way merge

if given undirect graph
if given item class with particular order
if ask to update all item into sort
- topological sort
